nodes.text: The Star of Kala'unn was a priceless artifact of the Twi'lek culture. When it was acquired by a notorious Duros named Cada Bliss, it greatly angered Bliss' old adversary Vette, who decided to get it back. Together with Darth Baras' Sith apprentice, Vette retrieved the Star of Kala'unn from him and later gave it over to her friend Taunt, so that she could pass it to a museum.
